02:47 Monday 09 November 2015 JST Oh my goodness Hugo is way faster than Middleman.
Here&rsquo;s my script which I run from my ~/journal directory to put most recent entries online:
#!/bin/bash echo &quot;pushing&quot; git push echo &quot;yayer&quot; cd ~/journal-hugo git submodule foreach git pull origin master echo &quot;building&quot; hugo echo &quot;deploying&quot; rsync -r public/* newrobnugen:/home/newrob/new.robnugen.com echo &quot;coming back&quot; cd ~/journal echo &quot;back jack&quot;  Thanks to https://fredrikloch.me/post/automatic_hugo_deploy/ for the rsync line.
